{"tid":2219384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑開有條路...又有人唔見銀包","createTime":"2020-09-26T22:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T00:38:52.000Z","uid":238587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"597be004e7ca2ade3ad7ebcfc1d1d721151d3fda","tid":2219384,"uid":238587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:35:16.000Z","msg":"尋日一起身就爛眼鏡，下晝就唔見銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無好心人有機會執到，而家真係欲哭無淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：9月26（星期六）<br />\n時間：下晝4點正左右<br />\n唔見地點：西貢北港/ 市中心或 新巴792m<br />\n款式：Secrid 藍色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PEEtmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PEEtmH.jpg&h=2caa0dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經同巴士公司報失，架車返到總站都無發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後去到要問人借錢返屋企...<br />\n就算得返証件都好，仲有無希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd754760c36e48da6d2d93741603e159de96f58","tid":2219384,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c143fd0339a61f459938c27f1d401c873d5091","tid":2219384,"uid":378657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:41:23.000Z","msg":"報晒失同去狗屋備左案未？"},{"pid":"db65ab0176b7c40e6aef89fcdcffc5fee3ef13fb","tid":2219384,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:42:02.000Z","msg":"陰公豬去西貢開心完咩都無"},{"pid":"f22482e0dbbb9ea348126486eb28dcbb5088217a","tid":2219384,"uid":238587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69c143fd0339a61f459938c27f1d401c873d5091","tid":2219384,"uid":378657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:41:23.000Z","msg":"報晒失同去狗屋備左